[SN]TITLE[SN]
Llanrumney fire murder victim named as Robert Sadler, 59

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man who died following a house fire in Cardiff has been named as 59-year-old Robert Sadler.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Police were called to Mr Sadler's home in Llanrumney Avenue, Llanrumney, at 04:30 GMT on Sunday.
A 27-year-old woman was arrested on suspicion of murder and is being detained under the Mental Health Act.
Mr Sadler's family is being supported by family liaison officers and South Wales Police is continuing to investigate his death.
